  <scopecontent id="aspace_fbf6c3601154daba281c1c7ffb246da0">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Two scrapbooks depicting the academic and social life of a Cornell University undergraduate, with particular reference to her courtship with Paul Atterdig (Cornell Class of 1946); includes photographs, clippings, ephemera, and other material with reference to the campus V-12 Program, and many other social activities.</p>  </scopecontent>
